data.description: Lovely Cape Cod updated and move in ready!   Enjoy an evening relaxing in the oversized living room in front of the fireplace complete with a beautiful gas insert.   Entertaining is a breeze when preparing the evening's menu in the wonderful kitchen on your very own granite countertops and then serving your guests in the lovely dining room.  Upstairs find 2 generous sized bedroom one with a quiet and cozy reading nook.  The finished basement has it's own egress window and a half bath; this space is perfect for privacy with all of the amenities.     This lovely home sits on a large lot with mature trees, space to garden, bird watch, and relax. New roof in 2020 new windows 2018
